Class ClanChiefModel

java.lang.Object
model.player.ClanChiefModel
public class ClanChiefModel extends Object
The model class for the ClanChiefModel object and game logic. Contains all the properties used by the operator to interact with it's environement, as examinePlace() or healAllCharacters().
